OL,5, Schools in England could face further  
OL,6, strike action as the National Education
OL,7, Union has asked teachers to reject a   
OL,8, new pay offer, after intensive talks.  
OL,10,FThe government has offered teachers a  
OL,11,F#1,000 extra cash payment this year and
OL,12,Fa 4.3% rise for most staff next year.  
OL,14,FMany teachers in England received a pay
OL,15,Frise of 5% in September 2022 but unions
OL,16,Fsay this was a cut due to inflation.   
OL,18,FThousands of schools were disrupted by 
OL,19,Fthe latest walkout by teachers who are 
OL,20,Fmembers of the NEU.                    
